<section id="idg-osoperator-osoperator-install-c-osooperate-xml-1">
 <title>Operation and Maintenance</title>
 <para>
  Regular operation and maintenance includes:
 </para>
 <itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Starting and stopping the agents.
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Disabling the monitoring of specific metrics in the configuration of a
    Metrics Agent.
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Disabling the collection of specific log data in the configuration of a Log
    Agent.
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Collecting the agent log files.
   </para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    Backup and recovery.
   </para>
  </listitem>
 </itemizedlist>
